    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it's like we're just trapped in this loop of trying to find meaning where there isn't any. if there's no point to the struggle, and everything just ends in the same nothingness anyway, then what's the actual difference between staying in this pain and just... letting go and embracing the void?",
